-- Taiwan's Fubon says looking at merger targets in China
-- By Emily Chan
-- Thu Mar 20, 2014 03:09AM EDT
-- None



TAIPEI, March 20 (Reuters) - Taiwan's Fubon Financial Holding Co Ltd <2881.TW> is considering acquiring brokerages in China's Anhui Province and Kunshan City, the firm's president told investors Thursday.

Taiwan and China have enjoyed warming ties in the financial sector over the past few years, opening the door to companies like Fubon to expand into mainland China.